Loop (MTLFP data)¶

Raw HyperFLow¶

%%time

df = []
alpha = 1e-7
lags = 11
r_all = {}
r2_all = {}
file = h5py.File(cfg.h_file, 'r')
for expt, grp in file.items():
    hf = np.array(grp['hyperflow'])
    spks = np.array(grp['spks'], dtype=float)
    good = ~np.array(grp['badspks'])
    good = np.where(good)[0]
    hf, spks = setup_supervised_data(lags, good, hf, spks)
    hf_r, spks_r = setup_repeat_data(grp, lags, 'hyperflowR')
    x = flatten_stim(hf)

    print(f"fitting {expt} . . .")
    for i in range(spks.shape[-1]):
        useful = i in cfg.useful_cells.get(expt, {})
        kf = KFold(5, shuffle=True, random_state=42)
        r_scores = []
        for fold, (trn, vld) in enumerate(kf.split(x)):
            mod = Ridge(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x[trn], spks[:, i][trn])
            pred = mod.predict(x[vld])
            nnll = null_adj_ll(spks[vld][:, i], np.abs(pred))
            r2 = r2_score(spks[vld][:, i], pred) * 100
            r, p = sp_stats.pearsonr(spks[vld][:, i], pred)
            print(f"{expt}, f{fold}.\tnnll = {nnll:0.3f},\tr2 = {r2:0.1f}%, r = {r:0.3f}")
            r_scores.append(r)
            df.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['nnll'],
                'score': [nnll],
            })
        r_all[f"{expt}_ch{i}"] = np.nanmean(r_scores)

        if spks_r is not None:
            mod = Ridge(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x, spks[:, i])
            pred = mod.predict(flatten_stim(hf_r))
            true = np.nanmean(spks_r, 1)[i]
            r2 = r2_score(true, pred) * 100
            r2_all[f"{expt}_ch{i}"] = r2
            df.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['r2'],
                'score': [r2],
            })
            plt.plot(true, label=f"{expt}, ch{i}.")
            plt.plot(pred, label=f"r2 = {r2:0.1f}%")
            plt.legend()
            plt.show()

        print('~' * 50)
    print('_' * 70 + '\n' + '_' * 70)
    print('\n\n')

df = pd.DataFrame(merge_dicts(df))
print('Done.')
file.close()

Reservoir approach (d=256)¶

rng = get_rng()
w = rng.normal(size=(8, 256))
plt.imshow(w, aspect=5);

%%time

df = []
alpha = 0.1
lags = 11
r_all = {}
r2_all = {}
file = h5py.File(cfg.h_file, 'r')
for expt, grp in file.items():
    hf = np.array(grp['hyperflow'])
    spks = np.array(grp['spks'], dtype=float)
    good = ~np.array(grp['badspks'])
    good = np.where(good)[0]
    hf, spks = setup_supervised_data(lags, good, hf, spks)
    hf_r, spks_r = setup_repeat_data(grp, lags, 'hyperflowR')
    # expand
    x = np.einsum('ijk, kl -> ijl', hf, w)
    x = flatten_stim(np.tanh(x))
    if hf_r is not None:
        x_r = np.einsum('ijk, kl -> ijl', hf_r, w)
        x_r = flatten_stim(np.tanh(x_r))

    print(f"fitting {expt} . . .")
    for i in range(spks.shape[-1]):
        useful = i in cfg.useful_cells.get(expt, {})
        kf = KFold(5, shuffle=True, random_state=42)
        r_scores = []
        for fold, (trn, vld) in enumerate(kf.split(x)):
            mod = Ridge(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x[trn], spks[:, i][trn])
            pred = mod.predict(x[vld])
            nnll = null_adj_ll(spks[vld][:, i], np.abs(pred))
            r2 = r2_score(spks[vld][:, i], pred) * 100
            r, p = sp_stats.pearsonr(spks[vld][:, i], pred)
            print(f"{expt}, f{fold}.\tnnll = {nnll:0.3f},\tr2 = {r2:0.1f}%, r = {r:0.3f}")
            r_scores.append(r)
            df.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['nnll'],
                'score': [nnll],
            })
        r_all[f"{expt}_ch{i}"] = np.nanmean(r_scores)

        if spks_r is not None:
            mod = Ridge(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x, spks[:, i])
            pred = mod.predict(x_r)
            true = np.nanmean(spks_r, 1)[i]
            r2 = r2_score(true, pred) * 100
            r2_all[f"{expt}_ch{i}"] = r2
            df.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['r2'],
                'score': [r2],
            })
            plt.plot(true, label=f"{expt}, ch{i}.")
            plt.plot(pred, label=f"r2 = {r2:0.1f}%")
            plt.legend()
            plt.show()

        print('~' * 50)
    print('_' * 70 + '\n' + '_' * 70)
    print('\n\n')

df = pd.DataFrame(merge_dicts(df))
print('Done.')
file.close()
